  "text": "A taxonomy can be described as a classification that uses ontology with primary purpose of providing basis for processing, communicating and reasoning about the cyber-related threats [CITATION_1] . Intelligence gathering has become one of the key aspect for successful defence against cyber-attacks, and taxonomies can play an essential part in supporting security experts to achieve this [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] . In the following we review previous taxonomies produced by scholars on different variants of malware.",
